findings.title: Deployer can mint after initial deployment
findings.description: The deployer has the ability to mint tokens even after the initial deployment.

findings.title: Deployer cannot block user
findings.description: The deployer does not have the capability to block or unblock users.

findings.title: Deployer can burn
findings.description: The deployer has the ability to burn tokens or assets, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Deployer cannot pause contract
findings.description: The deployer does not have the capability to pause the contract.
